summary: Super Eagles captain Mikel Obi escapes flight mishap after faulty Middlesbrough plane was grounded before take off
title: Super Eagles captain Mikel Obi escapes flight mishap after faulty Middlesbrough plane was grounded before take off
body:
Super Eagles captain Mikel Obi escapes flight mishap after faulty Middlesbrough plane was grounded before take off

The flight of Mikel and his Middlesbrough teammates had to be cancelled after a fear of a possible plane crash.

Super Eagles captain, Mikel Obi and his Middlesbrough teammates have reportedly escaped a possible plane crash.

The 31-year-old Mikel Obi who joined Championship side Middlesbrough on a short term deal was reportedly at risk of a plane crash just after their game…
